BTCSERV.net is a free for all [[Mining_Pool]] with proportional [[Bitcoin]] payouts located in Germany. The pool has launched on July 9th, 2011 and its features are [[Long_Polling]], SSL encrypted user interface and fast payouts. At present, only the [[transaction fee|transaction_fees]] are kept by the pool operator.

